twoSetSkill.name: Spectral Jet 2 Pieces
twoSetSkill.description: Basic ATKs (including Combo and Charged ATKs) have a 10% chance to inflict one the following debuffs for 6.0s: paralyze, freeze, stun, slow, ignite, impair, and weaken. CD: 2.0s.

threeSetSkill.name: Deadly Acceleration 3 Pieces
threeSetSkill.description: For every 1.0s, Basic ATK (including Combo and Charged ATKs) gains 20% Total DMG Multiplier. Stacks up to 5 times. Attacking resets the buff and initiates a 7s CD.
